{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/office-for-the-internal-market/about/media-enquiries","content_id":"b2698949-4773-4940-ad8a-fa8b620eb395","description":"Contact the CMA press office if you’re a journalist with a media enquiry about the OIM. ","details":{"attachments":[],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>If you are a member of the media and would like to speak to someone about the OIM and / or its work, please contact the CMA media team who are acting on behalf of the OIM.</p>\n\n<p>Journalists with enquiries can call the CMA’s press team between 9am to 5:30pm, Monday to Friday by:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>phone: 020 3738 6460</li>\n  <li>email: <a href=\"mailto:press@cma.gov.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\">press@cma.gov.uk</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>If you are not a member of the media, please contact the CMA general enquiries team by:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>phone: (020 3738 6000)</li>\n  <li>email: <a href=\"mailto:general.enquiries@cma.gov.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\">general.enquiries@cma.gov.uk</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n</div>","change_history":[{"note":"First published.","public_timestamp":"2021-09-21T10:02:22Z"}],"organisation":"b1123ceb-77e4-40fc-9526-83ad0ba7cf01","tags":{"browse_pages":[]}},"document_type":"media_enquiries","first_published_at":"2021-09-21T11:02:22+01:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/office-for-the-internal-market/about/media-enquiries","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/office-for-the-internal-market/about/media-enquiries","base_path":"/government/organisations/office-for-the-internal-market/about/media-enquiries","content_id":"b2698949-4773-4940-ad8a-fa8b620eb395","document_type":"media_enquiries","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2021-09-21T10:02:22Z","schema_name":"corporate_information_page","title":"Media enquiries","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/office-for-the-internal-market/about/media-enquiries","w